'''限時限額加碼停利投資法'''（{{lang-en|'''E'''nhanced '''D'''ollar '''C'''ost '''A'''veraging}}，{{lang|en|'''EDCA'''}}），是改良自[[平均成本法|平均成本法]]的一套系統化投資方法，以達成投資人投資獲利的目標。<ref name = "DSpace CRIS_2020"> {{ cite web | title = DSpace CRIS | url = https://scholars.lib.ntu.edu.tw/handle/123456789/107544 | publisher = 臺灣大學: 企業管理碩士專班 | language = zh-tw | date = 2012 }} </ref><ref name = "Lee Dunham and Geoffrey C. Friesen_2019">{{cite web | title = Building a Better Mousetrap: Enhanced Dollar Cost Averaging | url = https://digitalcommons.unl.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1025&context=financefacpub | author = Lee Dunham and Geoffrey C. Friesen | date = 2011-12 | access-date = 2020-12-09 | archive-date = 2020-12-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201203110123/https://digitalcommons.unl.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1025&context=financefacpub | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== EDCA 投資流程 ==
依據市場波動大小決定定時投入資金的變動百分比 Y<ref name = "Lee Dunham and Geoffrey C. Friesen_2019" />
* 當投資標的前一個月下跌時，本月投資金額加碼 Y% 金額
* 當投資標的前一個月上漲時，本月投資金額減碼 Y% 金額



